sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant UI as Chrome Extension (User A)
    participant API as Node.js Gateway
    participant UN as User RLN Node (Sender)
    participant MN as Master RLN Node (Receiver)
    participant PX as RGB Proxy Server

    Note over UN, MN: Lightning Channel Open (9 PHO / 1 PHO split)

    UI->>API: POST /pay-lightning (invoice, wallet_key)
    API->>UN: Command: send_payment(invoice)
    
    rect rgb[#fff3cd]
    Note right of UN: Off-Chain Payment Logic
    UN->>MN: HTLC / Payment Hash Update (Lightning)
    MN-->>UN: Pre-image / Receipt (Instant)
    end

    rect rgb[#d1ecf1]
    Note over UN, PX: RGB Metadata Sync
    UN->>PX: Upload PHO Consignment (Proof of 1 PHO transfer)
    MN->>PX: Download & Validate Consignment
    end

    UN->>API: Payment Success (Hash: 69018fc3...)
    API->>UI: Update Balance: 8.00 PHO
    
    Note over UI: UI shows "Settled" in < 1 second
